## Key Technical Decisions

- **Framework:** Remix + TypeScript
- **Package Manager:** Bun
- **Storage:** S3-compatible (R2, S3, MinIO)
- **Images:** Cloudflare Image Resizing / Sharp
- **Deploy:** Multi-platform (Cloudflare, Docker, AWS)
